snippet.title: ROMANCELVANIA - a loving parody of Metroidvanias - Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Please help support Romancelvania and The Deep End Games via our Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thedeependgames/romancelvania

Slay or lay?

It's Castlevania meets The Bachelor!

This thirsty metroidvania marries classic action RPG gameplay with base building, reality TV, & romance!

Follow the campaign, back us if you can, or just help us spread the word! 

Discord: https://discord.gg/ytPd3vp
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheDeepEndGames
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thedeependga...
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/deependgames/

http://www.thedeependgames.com/
